SUMMARY:Rules-Light RPGs
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nChange your PRIVACY SETTINGS so I can actually reply to your messages! :)\n\nor contact me directly at\nemail = God.Emperor@Gmail.com\ncall/text = 971 325-2100\n\nJoin us on Thursdays for Spacy weird Fantasy\, or Mörk Borg/Pirates\, or Call of Cthulhu\, and other One-Shots -- things change over time.\n\nSo send me an email at God.Emperor@Gmail.com or call/text me at 971 325-2100 for more setting and system info. And the story plots are episodic enough that you can miss sessions and it's no big deal.
