SUMMARY:Board Game Club @ Langer's
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nCome play games and meet other local gamers at Langer's Entertainment Center in Sherwood! Bring your own games or pick from a wide selection brought by others. Admission is free and family-friendly. Food can be purchased through Langer's. Attendance averages 20 people.
