SUMMARY:ACC Cribbage Club
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nThis is an ACC "grass roots" club.\n\nThe American Cribbage Congress (ACC) is a national organization that sponsors tournaments and grass roots clubs\, and standardizes rules.\n\nYou will play 6 games against 6 different opponents.\n\nThe money collected from entry fees is paid out to the top finishers.\n\nRecommended for experienced intermediate/advanced players.\n\nYou should be able to finish a game in less than 20 minutes.\n\nThere will be players there who are not from Meetup\, so even when there are few RSVP's\, you can be sure we will play.
