SUMMARY:Southeast Portland Board Games and Cards
DESCRIPTION:Portland Area Board Games and RPGs\nA place to relive an old favorite or try a brand new game. We meet every Saturday and usually split into 2-3 groups for variety of game play. You are welcome to bring your favorite game (or games) or jump in and learn something new with us. We have a wide selection of games that are sure to satisfy and excite.\n\nCome solo\, come with a friend\, come for half an hour or 3 hours - just come ready to meet someone new\, share some laughs\, and get lost in a game. We value community\, new connections\, and laughing together.\n\nSee you there! Look for the group with games on the table.\n\n*Previously under SE Portland Board Games and Cards meetup group\, we are moving to this meetup group for this coming year. To stay updated please join our facebook group: https://www.facebook.com/share/g/1Ys4dEAvqo/.*
